title: Jessie James Decker Loves BellyBuds by WavHello
description:
Country singer and entrepreneur, Jessie James Decker, explains why she loves BellyBuds by WavHello. Jessie and her husband, NFL player Eric Decker, used BellyBuds baby bump speakers to play music and special messages to the womb when she was pregnant with their son, Eric Jr. ! 

BellyBuds are specialized speakers that gently adhere to your belly and safely play music and voice messages to baby in the womb!
